title: Can I afford to go Organic?
description:
Jillian says, 'You bet there is!'  Then Jillian jumps right into questions from listeners dealing with diet, fitness, nutrition, inspiration, plus a call that some of our guy listeners may be dealing with, and that's peaking potassium.
